â€œUse a substitute object to control access to a real one.â€

Instead of interacting with the actual object, the client talks to a proxy that acts on its behalf.

ğŸ§ª Real-World Analogy
Think of a security guard outside a private vault:
- You donâ€™t access the vault directly.
- The guard checks credentials and then lets you in. That guard is a proxy to the vault.
